 		<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">With the number of seniors growing, the U.S. stumbles toward a day of reckoning</h1>
 		<h5 class="byline"><span class="by-author"><span class="by">By</span> <span class="author vcard" itemprop="author"><a class="url fn n" href="https://nmpolitics.net/index/author/kent-paterson/" title="More from Kent Paterson" rel="author">Kent Paterson</a></span></span><span class="sep"> | </span><time class="entry-date updated dtstamp pubdate" datetime="2017-08-25T06:35:24-06:00">August 25, 2017</time></h5>

